{"type":"message","id":"4b3f6939","parentId":"70d447bc","timestamp":"2026-03-20T09:23:55.020Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Current Settings:**\n\n| Setting | Value |\n|---------|-------|\n| **Default model** | `minimax-m2.5:cloud` |\n| **Fallbacks** | `minimax-m2.5:cloud` → `nemotron-3-super:cloud` |\n| **Context window** | 128000 tokens (minimax) / 131072 (nemotron) |\n| **Compaction mode** | `safeguard` |\n\n**No explicit token limit set** — the context window comes from the model definitions. The `safeguard` compaction mode means it only compacts when nearing the limit, not proactively.\n\nWant me to adjust any of these?"}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":18044,"output":254,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18298,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1773998635019}}
