{"type":"message","id":"8efd1f0b","parentId":"0a3f1cd0","timestamp":"2026-03-20T09:53:10.905Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here's what I found:\n\n---\n\n## Compaction Settings\n\n| Path | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| `agents.defaults.compaction.mode` | `\"safeguard\"` |\n| `models.providers.ollama.models[*].contextWindow` | **60,000** (all models) |\n| `models.providers.ollama.models[*].maxTokens` | 8,192 – 128,000 |\n\n---\n\n## What These Mean\n\n- **`mode: safeguard`** → Only compacts when hitting the hard limit (contextWindow)\n- **No `targetSize`** → No proactive compaction at a percentage or token count\n- **No `reserveTokens`** → Not configured\n- **No `threshold`** → Not configured (tried adding before, caused config error)\n\n---\n\n## The Problem\n\nWith contextWindow at **60,000** and `safeguard` mode, compaction triggers when you hit 60k tokens. But that's AFTER the session has grown large — not at 70% like you wanted.\n\nThere's no proactive target. Want me to explain what options exist for making compaction more proactive?"}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":38874,"output":370,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39244,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1774000390903}}
