{"type":"message","id":"98bb82d5","parentId":"e3d21af5","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:03:07.257Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_13faad6f-d05c-4940-939e-eb3e67593238","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"OpenClaw config \\\"session.scope\\\" per-sender global tui configuration\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 2,\n  \"tookMs\": 1415,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"brave\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e40aa0d77e2a15fc\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSession Tools - OpenClaw\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e40aa0d77e2a15fc\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://docs.openclaw.ai/concepts/session-tool\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f198c6dd7addcbb9\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nNode sessions use node-&lt;nodeId&gt; unless explicitly set. global and unknown are reserved values and are never listed. <strong>If session.scope = &quot;global&quot;, we alias it to main for all tools so callers never see global</strong>.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f198c6dd7addcbb9\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"docs.openclaw.ai\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ae79fd0fae27ed03\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSession Tools - OpenClaw Docs | Learn OpenClaw\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ae79fd0fae27ed03\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.learnclawdbot.org/docs/concepts/session-tool\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"594c3cb0755fa3f6\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n<strong>If session.scope = &quot;global&quot;, we alias it to main for all tools so callers never see global</strong>. List sessions as an array of rows. ... Tool results are filtered out in list output; use sessions_history for tool messages.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"594c3cb0755fa3f6\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.learnclawdbot.org\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"OpenClaw config \"session.scope\" per-sender global tui configuration","provider":"brave","count":2,"tookMs":1415,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"brave","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"e40aa0d77e2a15fc\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nSession Tools - OpenClaw\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"e40aa0d77e2a15fc\">>>","url":"https://docs.openclaw.ai/concepts/session-tool","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f198c6dd7addcbb9\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nNode sessions use node-&lt;nodeId&gt; unless explicitly set. global and unknown are reserved values and are never listed. <strong>If session.scope = &quot;global&quot;, we alias it to main for all tools so callers never see global</strong>.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f198c6dd7addcbb9\">>>","siteName":"docs.openclaw.ai"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"ae79fd0fae27ed03\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nSession Tools - OpenClaw Docs | Learn OpenClaw\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"ae79fd0fae27ed03\">>>","url":"https://www.learnclawdbot.org/docs/concepts/session-tool","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"594c3cb0755fa3f6\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n<strong>If session.scope = &quot;global&quot;, we alias it to main for all tools so callers never see global</strong>. List sessions as an array of rows. ... Tool results are filtered out in list output; use sessions_history for tool messages.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"594c3cb0755fa3f6\">>>","siteName":"www.learnclawdbot.org"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774000987255}}
{"type":"message","id":"16ffefc3","parentId":"98bb82d5","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:03:09.099Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_ef661ab5-c941-45ad-9f2d-838c3c0bcfab","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"OpenClaw \"session\" configuration scope dmScope mainKey","count":10}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":37625,"output":58,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37683,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1774000989098}}
{"type":"message","id":"e853da1a","parentId":"16ffefc3","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:03:11.174Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_ef661ab5-c941-45ad-9f2d-838c3c0bcfab","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"OpenClaw \\\"session\\\" configuration scope dmScope mainKey\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 10,\n  \"tookMs\": 2070,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"brave\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"1a6991f0fc10aed4\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSession Management - OpenClaw\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"1a6991f0fc10aed4\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://docs.openclaw.ai/concepts/session\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"9ef6dc95fde3b3de\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nDirect chats follow session.dmScope (default main). <strong>main: agent:&lt;agentId&gt;:&lt;mainKey&gt;</strong> (continuity across devices/channels).\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"9ef6dc95fde3b3de\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"docs.openclaw.ai\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0c7cf1b7ae12d588\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSession Management | Openclaw Docs\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0c7cf1b7ae12d588\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://openclaw.im/docs/concepts/session\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b95c460d15467c29\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n// ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json { session: { scope: &quot;per-sender&quot;, // keep group keys separate dmScope: &quot;main&quot;, // DM continuity (set per-channel-peer/per-account-channel-peer for shared inboxes) identityLinks: { alice: [&quot;telegram:123456789&quot;, &quot;discord:987654321012345678&quot;], }, reset: { // Defaults: mode=daily, atHour=4 (gateway host local time).\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b95c460d15467c29\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"openclaw.im\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b26e5d224056dc6f\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nOpenClaw: docs/concepts/session.md | Fossies\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b26e5d224056dc6f\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://fossies.org/linux/openclaw/docs/concepts/session.md\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a7d23262703fad9c\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nOpenClaw treats one direct-chat session per agent as primary. Direct chats collapse to agent:<strong>&lt;agentId&gt;:&lt;mainKey&gt; (default main),</strong> while group/channel chats get their own keys. session.mainKey is honored. Use session.dmScope to control how direct messages are grouped:\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a7d23262703fad9c\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"fossies.org\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"dfffdb86ed441775\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSession Management - OpenClaw Documentation\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"dfffdb86ed441775\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://open-claw.blog/docs/session.html\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ef911e4d39a6ddbc\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n// ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json { session: { scope: &quot;per-sender&quot;, // keep group keys separate dmScope: &quot;main&quot;, // DM continuity (set per-channel-peer/per-account-channel-peer for shared inboxes) identityLinks: { alice: [&quot;telegram:123456789&quot;, &quot;discord:987654321012345678&quot;], }, reset: { // Defaults: mode=daily, atHour=4 (gateway host local time).\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ef911e4d39a6ddbc\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"open-claw.blog\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b491178d3528d6c3\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSession Scoping & Isolation - Introduction to OpenClaw | Stanza\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b491178d3528d6c3\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.stanza.dev/courses/openclaw/sessions-memory/openclaw-session-scoping-isolation\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ddc6fe29d2d8ed6a\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nDMScope — controls how direct-message sessions are partitioned across peers and channels. Session Key — <strong>a deterministic string that uniquely identifies a session, following the pattern agent:&lt;agentId&gt;:&lt;mainKey&gt;</strong>.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ddc6fe29d2d8ed6a\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.stanza.dev\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b8fd02142412e4aa\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSession Management | openclaw/openclaw | DeepWiki\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b8fd02142412e4aa\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://deepwiki.com/openclaw/openclaw/2.4-session-management\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f34681f66684d46e\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nDifferent dmScope values create entirely separate conversation contexts even for the same user and provider: Sources: src/routing/session-key.ts src/agents/pi-embedded-runner/run/attempt.ts606-611 · The session store maintains a registry mapping session keys to their metadata. Each SessionEntry contains: Sources: src/config/sessions.ts src/auto-reply/reply/agent-runner.ts256-284 · The session store is persisted to ~/.openclaw/state/sessions.json.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f34681f66684d46e\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"1 week ago\",\n      \"siteName\": \"deepwiki.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e6aabb0ee772eeae\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nConfiguration | Docs | OpenClaw\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e6aabb0ee772eeae\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://openclaws.io/docs/gateway/configuration\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ad999bda012b95e4\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSessions control conversation continuity and isolation: ```json5 { session: { dmScope: &quot;per-channel-peer&quot;, // recommended for multi-user threadBindings: { enabled: true, idleHours: 24, maxAgeHours: 0, }, reset: { mode: &quot;daily&quot;, atHour: 4, idleMinutes: 120, }, }, } ``` - `dmScope`: `main` (shared) | `per-peer` | `per-channel-peer` | `per-account-channel-peer` - `threadBindings`: global defaults for thread-bound session routing (Discord supports `/focus`, `/unfocus`, `/agents`, `/session idle`, and `/session max-age`).\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ad999bda012b95e4\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"openclaws.io\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f38bbc652fa288d1\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nConfiguration | OpenClaw Docs\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f38bbc652fa288d1\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://openclaw-ai.com/en/docs/gateway/configuration\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"39424f9fc079dd9d\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n```json5 { session: { dmScope: &quot;per-channel-peer&quot;, // recommended for multi-user threadBindings: { enabled: true, ttlHours: 24, }, reset: { mode: &quot;daily&quot;, atHour: 4, idleMinutes: 120, }, }, } ``` - `dmScope`: `main` (shared) | `per-peer` | `per-channel-peer` | `per-account-channel-peer` - `threadBindings`: global defaults for thread-bound session routing (Discord supports `/focus`, `/unfocus`, `/agents`, and `/session ttl`).\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"39424f9fc079dd9d\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"openclaw-ai.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"7e72227ab2aab411\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nOpenClaw Session Keys and Routing Deep Dive | OpenClaw Blog\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"7e72227ab2aab411\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://openclawblog.space/articles/openclaw-session-keys-and-routing-deep-dive\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"7bace69a3daf2936\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n<strong>OpenClaw treats one direct-chat session per agent as primary while group/channel traffic maps into non-main session keys</strong>. This prevents group memory from polluting personal DMs by default[1]. ... In larger installs, each agent keeps isolated workspace/session state while channel account bindings ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"7bace69a3daf2936\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"4 weeks ago\",\n      \"siteName\": \"openclawblog.space\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b23e335a8310324f\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nFeishu DM ignores dmScope configuration and routes to agent:main:main · Issue #10172 · openclaw/openclaw\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b23e335a8310324f\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/10172\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"9925834dedf044e7\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nEnvironment OpenClaw version: 2026.2.3-1 OS: macOS 26.2 (arm64) Node: v25.2.1 Configuration { &quot;session&quot;: { &quot;dmScope&quot;: &quot;per-channel-peer&quot; } } Expected behavior Feishu DM messages should route to: agent:main:feishu:dm:ou_cba67b0c645b674a33...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"9925834dedf044e7\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"February 6, 2026\",\n      \"siteName\": \"github.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"OpenClaw \"session\" configuration scope dmScope mainKey","provider":"brave","count":10,"tookMs":2070,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"brave","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"1a6991f0fc10a