{"type":"message","id":"095a1503","parentId":"a9e5f0f4","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:03:41.919Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_fd65a21c-a06d-4e8e-8954-af8a002c70c5","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"OpenClaw \\\"tui-\\\" session key generate UUID each connection TUI client default session\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 1,\n  \"tookMs\": 1491,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"brave\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8624eee3310adf06\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n[Bug] /session command doesn't create session until first message sent · Issue #5931 · openclaw/openclaw\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8624eee3310adf06\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/5931\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"5aa35eca5e77896e\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n<strong>/session &lt;name&gt;</strong> only updates the client-side session key (stored in localStorage for webchat, or in state for TUI). The session entry is not created in sessions.json until there&#x27;s actual activity (message sent/received).\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"5aa35eca5e77896e\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"February 1, 2026\",\n      \"siteName\": \"github.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"OpenClaw \"tui-\" session key generate UUID each connection TUI client default session","provider":"brave","count":1,"tookMs":1491,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"brave","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8624eee3310adf06\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n[Bug] /session command doesn't create session until first message sent · Issue #5931 · openclaw/openclaw\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8624eee3310adf06\">>>","url":"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/5931","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5aa35eca5e77896e\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n<strong>/session &lt;name&gt;</strong> only updates the client-side session key (stored in localStorage for webchat, or in state for TUI). The session entry is not created in sessions.json until there&#x27;s actual activity (message sent/received).\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5aa35eca5e77896e\">>>","published":"February 1, 2026","siteName":"github.com"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774001021915}}
