07e8b1c9d9d717e8\">>>","published":"January 20, 2026","siteName":"github.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"37f5376fc0fa319f\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n[Bug] /session command doesn't create session until first message sent · Issue #5931 · openclaw/openclaw\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"37f5376fc0fa319f\">>>","url":"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/5931","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f043b64a07d92ecf\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nThe new sessions are not visible until you send a message to them. <strong>/session &lt;name&gt; only updates the client-side session key</strong> (stored in localStorage for webchat, or in state for TUI).\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f043b64a07d92ecf\">>>","published":"February 1, 2026","siteName":"github.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"38013eadde2525f9\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n[TUI] Sub-agent announce messages not rendered until next user input · Issue #30409 · openclaw/openclaw\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"38013eadde2525f9\">>>","url":"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/30409","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"52422361e03b8fdd\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nThe TUI also connects via WebSocket but appears to only render streaming events from the current active run. Sub-agent announces are injected as system messages into the main session — these may not trigger a TUI re-render when the TUI is in idle state (no active run streaming).\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"52422361e03b8fdd\">>>","published":"3 weeks ago","siteName":"github.com"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774001028755}}
{"type":"message","id":"005c5371","parentId":"d524b7e4","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:03:53.247Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**FOUND IT! 🎯** \n\nFrom the Chinese docs (official OpenClaw!):\n```\n会话范围：\n- per-sender（默认）：每个智能体有多个会话。\n- global：TUI 始终使用 global 会话（选择器可能为空）。\n```\n\nThis confirms the default is `per-sender` which creates a NEW session per TUI connection!\n\nLet me search for how to configure this:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_94589bef-11c2-4dd5-9cd1-832c59ea03b2","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"OpenClaw config \"session.scope\" global setting tui","count":10}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":35210,"output":309,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35519,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1774001033246}}
{"type":"message","id":"e30ef1e3","parentId":"005c5371","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:03:54.682Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_94589bef-11c2-4dd5-9cd1-832c59ea03b2","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"OpenClaw config \\\"session.scope\\\" global setting tui\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 1,\n  \"tookMs\": 1431,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"brave\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3720c83c148f355b\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSession Tools - OpenClaw\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3720c83c148f355b\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://docs.openclaw.ai/concepts/session-tool\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"bba386b64edab11d\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nNode sessions use node-&lt;nodeId&gt; unless explicitly set. global and unknown are reserved values and are never listed. If session.<strong>scope = &quot;global&quot;, we alias it to main for all tools so callers never see global</strong>.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"bba386b64edab11d\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"docs.openclaw.ai\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"OpenClaw config \"session.scope\" global setting tui","provider":"brave","count":1,"tookMs":1431,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"brave","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"3720c83c148f355b\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nSession Tools - OpenClaw\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"3720c83c148f355b\">>>","url":"https://docs.openclaw.ai/concepts/session-tool","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"bba386b64edab11d\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nNode sessions use node-&lt;nodeId&gt; unless explicitly set. global and unknown are reserved values and are never listed. If session.<strong>scope = &quot;global&quot;, we alias it to main for all tools so callers never see global</strong>.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"bba386b64edab11d\">>>","siteName":"docs.openclaw.ai"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774001034680}}
{"type":"message","id":"fc4e4bbb","parentId":"e30ef1e3","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:03:59.427Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_77d3213b-988b-48ac-85aa-0b79d12262dc","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat >> ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-20.md << 'EOF'\n\n## 12:10 SAST — ROOT CAUSE CONFIRMED & FIX FOUND\n\n**ROOT CAUSE:**\n- `session.scope` is NOT in config (defaults to \"per-sender\")\n- per-sender = each TUI connection creates NEW session with unique key\n- Sessions look like: `agent:main:tui-<uuid>` instead of `agent:main:main`\n\n**THE FIX:**\nAdd to openclaw.json:\n```json\n\"session\": {\n  \"scope\": \"global\"\n}\n```\n\nThis tells TUI to ALWAYS use the \"main\" session instead of creating new ones.\n\n**Evidence from official docs:**\n- \"per-sender (默认): 每个智能体有多个会话\" = \"per-sender (default): each agent has many sessions\"\n- \"global: TUI 始终使用 global 会话\" = \"global: TUI always uses global session\"\n\n**Awaiting user approval before implementing.**\nEOF\necho \"Stored\""}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":35657,"output":293,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35950,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1774001039427}}
