{"type":"message","id":"58ef1586","parentId":"f462f93a","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:08:34.927Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Yes, you'll need to reconnect your TUI** — but not a full reset.\n\nHere's what happens:\n1. **Implement the config change** (add `session.scope: \"global\"`)\n2. **Restart the Gateway** (or at minimum, restart your TUI)\n3. **Next TUI connection** → automatically uses `agent:main:main` instead of spawning `tui-<uuid>`\n\nYou won't lose the existing conversation — the \"main\" session already has your history. New connections just join that same session instead of creating fresh ones.\n\nWant me to:\n1. Backup the config\n2. Add the `session.scope: \"global\"` setting\n3. Restart the Gateway\n\n?"}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":43813,"output":367,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44180,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1774001314926}}
